{"tid":639158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[收回主權] 原來全國政協, 國務院, 國防部, 鄧小平都錯哂,  得楊局長係堅識野","createTime":"2018-04-23T09:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T14:43:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"276746bec7fcede4136d888e949d3ae840340a38","tid":639158,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"中國人民政治協商會議全國委員會(全國政協):<br />\n<br />\n(一國兩制)即&ldquo;一個國家，兩種制度&rdquo;的簡稱。中國共產黨和中國政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為了收回香港、澳門主權</span></strong></span>，實現台灣與祖國大陸統一而提出的一項重要戰略方針。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cppcc.gov.cn/2011/09/26/ARTI1317001118812175.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cppcc.gov.cn%2F2011%2F09%2F26%2FARTI1317001118812175.shtml&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlRzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=7927e88b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cppcc.gov.cn/2011/09/26/ARTI1317001118812175.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n1983年國務院政府工作報告<br />\n...我們還將在適當的時候<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>收回香港主權</strong></span></span>，並且採取適當措施維持香港繁榮。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.cn/test/2006-02/16/content_200823.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Ftest%2F2006-02%2F16%2Fcontent_200823.htm&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlRzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=a1d85b3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.cn/test/2006-02/16/content_200823.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中國幹部學習網:<br />\n自從香港淪陷並被割讓以來，祖國人民眷念香港同胞，從未放棄過<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>收回香港主權</strong></span></span>的努力。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ccln.gov.cn/xxzgyc/253653-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccln.gov.cn%2Fxxzgyc%2F253653-1.shtml&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlRzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=d9b3720a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ccln.gov.cn/xxzgyc/253653-1.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n中國國防部<br />\n&ldquo;一國&rdquo;體現了中國要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>收回香港主權</strong></span></span>的堅定決心，&ldquo;兩制&rdquo;則充分考慮了香港歷史的特殊性，充分調動了香港民眾的積極性，&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;的成功有其必然性。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mod.gov.cn/big5/jmsd/2017-07/01/content_4784333.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mod.gov.cn%2Fbig5%2Fjmsd%2F2017-07%2F01%2Fcontent_4784333.htm&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlRzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=42c51fbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mod.gov.cn/big5/jmsd/2017-07/01/content_4784333.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n在後來出版的《鄧小平》文選中，清晰記錄下了這次談話的內容，&ldquo;我先把中央已決定的原則與大家講一講，到1997年必須<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收回香港主權</span></strong></span>，這是原則問題，不可討論的，但對香港仍要繼續維持自由港，貿易金融中心不變，即根據憲法草案第三十條原對台灣的也可用之香港，使其繼續留在資本主義制度。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://phtv.ifeng.com/a/20170627/44643763_0.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphtv.ifeng.com%2Fa%2F20170627%2F44643763_0.shtml&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlRzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=21f272f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://phtv.ifeng.com/a/20170627/44643763_0.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇楊局長咁既人才, 唔知又要錯多幾多十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後生可畏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f656b25c37a86334f5315d5c1b04585c19839051","tid":639158,"uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:47:49.000Z","msg":"中國或成為最大的贏家"},{"pid":"c5e1d9718c3bff57c26d4388474bb1a099305673","tid":639158,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"中英談判是錯的"},{"pid":"d392e88af484240cc4c3d8dcf333c62c76c90a38","tid":639158,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f597aeb51ba29ace461fcb0a9c1b78910a94fb6","tid":639158,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"Cap埋圖啦 <br />\nShare都易D"},{"pid":"4770543340b81d794d8b6bf1c330541da7696821","tid":639158,"uid":85116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"不得了,反黨反革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3356339526358bf9cd331b68aa921a23c06b3096","tid":639158,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"超班馬屁精"},{"pid":"68cc317d3d1f819896e68d00d503f855e9d1a996","tid":639158,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"可悲到連 主權移交 咁中性咁精準既描述都要改，根本就係篡改歷史。"},{"pid":"98ae11b49ef13b2a3d28a5eb5610d3164cedb6cb","tid":639158,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"屎忽鬼擦鞋之前都唔做定功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0053f5174b730489dfdff638aafe1fbe89ae21","tid":639158,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"基本法都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n序言<br />\n<br />\n香港自古以來就是中國的領土，一八四○年鴉片戰爭以後被英國佔領。一九八四年十二月十九日，中英兩國政府簽署了關於香港問題的聯合聲明，確認中華人民共和國政府於一九九七年七月一日恢復對香港行使主權，<span style=\"color: red;\">從而實現了長期以來中國人民收回香港的共同願望</span>。"}]}